      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;script---function&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Script - Function&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#script---function&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;savebysheetname&#34;&gt;&#xA;  savebysheetname&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#savebysheetname&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;image-container_48&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mcjoi/img1-repo/main/48x48/icon21_1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;savebysheetname&#34; title=&#34;savebysheetname&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;Save each sheet as a separate file.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;coloredrowdel&#34;&gt;&#xA;  coloredRowDel&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#coloredrowdel&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;image-container_48&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mcjoi/img1-repo/main/48x48/icon29_1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;coloredRowDel&#34; title=&#34;coloredRowDel&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;Delete the row of the colored cell from the selected area.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;handling-duplication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Handling Duplication&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#handling-duplication&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;checkduplication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  checkDuplication&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#checkduplication&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;image-container_48&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mcjoi/img1-repo/main/48x48/icon27_1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;checkduplication&#34; title=&#34;checkduplication&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;In the selected area, color the redundant value.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;removeduplicates&#34;&gt;&#xA;  removeDuplicates&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#removeduplicates&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;